{"tid":1157072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★三十幾年前metoo 視障女童，被裁定罪名成立","createTime":"2019-05-16T04:23:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T12:09:47.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"069146b0db264940bea94674ae85531974b8c3ae","tid":1157072,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T04:23:33.000Z","msg":"Now新聞台】康橋之家前院長張健華涉嫌三十多年前非禮一名視障女童，被裁定五項非禮罪罪名成立。<br />\n<br />\n張健華抵達區域法院聽取裁決，他早前被裁定表證成立，暫委法官練錦鴻指，事主性格害羞，沒有求助是合理，不會削弱證供的可信性，看不到事主有動機誣蔑被告。<br />\n<br />\n法官又認為被告張健華的證供很多地方顯露出不盡不實，亦誇大自己的視障問題，法官不排除他的視力遜於常人，但被告說謊的唯一理由是誇大以脫罪，因此不接納被告的供詞。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，他於1982至86年任職視障學校的活動助理期間，先後在學校圖書館、梯間﹑康樂室及游泳池等非禮一名視障女童，案件押後至6月6日判刑。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=348169\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D348169&d=nKoZ4xrs0zkQ%2F022jTHdf8F4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=3209b74e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D348169&h=75307f59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=348169</a>"},{"pid":"2c6891e0c71434cc198534ecb552f19991710058","tid":1157072,"uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T04:24:55.000Z","msg":"有冇八十年前 日軍metoo?"},{"pid":"70b5e1629ce3ba91e72cd7bfd98f3101e58ade33","tid":1157072,"uid":249885,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T04:36:35.000Z","msg":"口同鼻拗 寧縱無枉"},{"pid":"a984c16d46c48d9697e7a173b9e239026d5ebc1f","tid":1157072,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T04:41:07.000Z","msg":"有冇人證物證？乜都無，靠受害者講都告得入就好撚恐怖"},{"pid":"c017439b24e1141f3f39452ca6aa5e5322c3d947","tid":1157072,"uid":55914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T04:41:46.000Z","msg":"看不到事主有動機誣蔑被告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee7d4e4bf73a5f1260fa4d008f267779f206fb34","t